WP : TrendWager « the first prediction market for brc20 »


For BRC20 token assets, our platform functions as a decentralized prediction market. We want to provide customers a whimsical, thrilling, and decentralized platform where they may forecast future price changes for BRC20 token assets.
Users can receive incentives by correctly predicting whether the asset's price will increase or decrease. Users now have a new method to engage in the bitcoin market and maybe make money depending on their forecasts.
We created our platform to be entertaining, thrilling, and decentralized. Decentralization, in our opinion, is essential to making sure that people have total control over their money and may take part without depending on centralized authority.

How it works:


When the "LIVE" phase begins, users select a BRC20 token asset and forecast whether the price will be greater or lower than the current price. This enables users to base their forecasts on the state of the market.
Forecasts are fixed for five minutes. This guarantees that users cannot alter their predictions midway during the "LIVE" period and also gives the prediction market a sense of excitement and expectation.
The user wins if, at the end of the LIVE phase, the "Closed Price" is greater than the "Locked Price" and they correctly predicted that the price would increase. Users are encouraged to produce accurate forecasts as a result, and good predictions are clearly rewarded.


The user wins if, at the end of the LIVE phase, the "Closed Price" is lower than the "Locked Price" and they correctly predicted that the price would decline. Users now have two choices for making predictions and perhaps earning incentives.
Coins are used to pay out rewards. Users may simply withdraw and spend their rewards in the larger bitcoin ecosystem thanks to this.


Benefits of our platform:

Our platform offers consumers a fresh method to engage with cryptocurrencies in a pleasant and entertaining way. In our opinion, a pleasant and interesting platform will draw more people and offer a satisfying experience to all users.
Because of the decentralized nature of our platform, users may engage without relying on centralized authority and have complete control over their money. Compared to centralized prediction markets, this offers customers a higher level of confidentiality and anonymity.
Our platform uses the BRC20 token standard and is quick and safe. Decentralized prediction markets are a good fit for the trusted and popular BRC20 token standard. This guarantees the quickness and security of our platform.


Conclusion

Our platform is a ground-breaking and fascinating innovation in the bitcoin prediction market space. We think that our platform will promote greater use of cryptocurrencies and give people a fresh method to interact with them.
We give customers a quick and safe means to forecast future price fluctuations of BRC20 token assets by utilizing the BRC20 token standard and offering a decentralized platform. This guarantees that consumers may take part in the prediction market with security and confidence.


